data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
A hospital management system is a software designed to
manage all the areas of a hospital such as medical, financial,
administrative and the corresponding processing of services.
Hospital Management is a term very broad in scope and may
be defined from different aspects. It mainly relates to management
of all aspects of a hospital; a coordination of all elements of a hospital.
This may range from patient care to record keeping to inventory of medicines and staffs.
